text: Sundsvalls SS is a Swedish swim team from Sundsvall training in Sporthallsbadet. == Olympics == The team's most famous swimmers are Olympic gold medalist for 100m Butterfly Lars Frölander and Olympic bronze medalist Anna-Karin Kammerling. ==Swimmers== *Lars Frölander (1996-2001) *Anna-Karin Kammerling ==External links== *Sundsvalls SS's official homepage Category:Swimming clubs in Sweden Category:Sport in Sundsvall
title: Sundsvalls SS
